<refsect1>
	<title>Description</title>
	<para>
		&p; locks the entire virtual console system, completely disabling all
		console access. It gives up these locks when either the password of
		the user who started ulock or the root password is typed. &p; is able
		to invoke any program (i.e. screen saver), which will be terminated on
		any keystroke.
	</para>
</refsect1>

<refsect1>
	<title>Options</title>
	<para>
		&p; accepts the following options:
	</para>

	<variablelist>
		<varlistentry>
			<term><option><replaceable>command</replaceable></option></term>
